title: Liquid-phase xylene isomerization on nano-sized ZSM-5
content:
RSC Adv., 2024, 14,19264-19270
DOI: 10.1039/D4RA02828G, Paper

Peixi Feng, Chenglin Kang, Xin Yue, Zhenhuan Zhou, Zhongxun Liu, Yueting Gai, Junjun Shi, Baoning Zong
Liquid-phase xylene isomerization was conducted using nanometer ZSM-5, which was synthesized with TPAOH as the SDA and S-1 as the seed. The catalyst exhibited high catalytic activity and selectivity.
